  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/a3192d9429fde6fc9162dae9c0b7b539.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>BattleParty is a 2D survival co-op game in an apocalyptic world. Your only goal, to survive as long as possible!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/fb1767204a80e64ef757e831282c664b.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>Grrrr! Do you hear them too? The zombies ! Your only worst enemies, if they catch you, they will devour you! Do not allow yourself to be fooled, look for what to defend yourself: weapon, grenade, rocket launcher or even your grandma if necessary! If you have nothing on hand, run as fast as you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/2ebefc226eb06e851be99ec52049497a.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>You've guessed, we will gave you weapons, there is something for everyone!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/ad584557f40d0f41a3b207929033980d.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>It's not enough? Okay, very good, well you also have vehicles, hell yeaah!! With that, you can move faster, and even crush a few zombies, but be very careful with your fuel gauge!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/a3192d9429fde6fc9162dae9c0b7b539.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>BattleParty is a 2D survival co-op game in an apocalyptic world. Your only goal, to survive as long as possible!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/fb1767204a80e64ef757e831282c664b.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>Grrrr! Do you hear them too? The zombies ! Your only worst enemies, if they catch you, they will devour you! Do not allow yourself to be fooled, look for what to defend yourself: weapon, grenade, rocket launcher or even your grandma if necessary! If you have nothing on hand, run as fast as you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/2ebefc226eb06e851be99ec52049497a.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>You've guessed, we will gave you weapons, there is something for everyone!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289500/extras/ad584557f40d0f41a3b207929033980d.webp?t=1587996674\" width=500 height=54 /></span><br>It's not enough? Okay, very good, well you also have vehicles, hell yeaah!! With that, you can move faster, and even crush a few zombies, but be very careful with your fuel gauge!",
